<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Quicktix - Activation Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    h2 {
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    p {
      color: #666666;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .otp {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333333;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello <%= user.name %>,</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Quicktix! To activate your account, please use the following OTP:</p>
    <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
    <p>If you did not request this activation, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing Quicktix!</p>
    <p>
      Regards,<br>
      The Quicktix Team
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>